<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ni vak achun chieh in, vak hawihtak achun,
 Zing khawvak hawih ahim, leh zan dai lakah;
 Awl a masuon zelin, nichenga pangin,
 Lam chenga Isu zuiin.

[V2]
 Zuiin, Isu chuh zui hitiu,
 Zuiin, nichengin zuiin;
 Zuiin, ei puihna mun chengah,
 Isu chuh lam cheng ah zui hitiu.

[V3]
 2. Nisat vanglai ahim, zan thimin ahim,
 Chavang hun nuom ahim nipi ahim in;
 Hukdampa sapna he'n awi dingin kinin,
 Lam chengah Isu zuiin.

[V4]
 3. Sana nivak ahim, leh mun lim achun,
 Huihpi hat lai ahim, a haih tieng ahim;
 A zahngaihna gingcha'n ni beihna chengin,
 Lam chengah Isu zuiin.</lyrics>
<title>WALKING IN THE SUNSHINE</title>
<hymn_number>172</hymn_number>
</song>